            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Wow...that's such a big flower...!<CR>I've never seen a flower this big before..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "extra_id": 0x1d9,
            "expr_id": 0x1,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Whoaaa, that's amazing! This is the biggest flower I've ever seen!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "(Huh? Is that...Nio's voice? How many years has it been since I've heard her?)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "(Oh no! I need to hurry up and talk to<CR>her!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Sis... *yawn* Good morning."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1d4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Huh? Where am I?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "This is Salt Desert. It's way to the west of the workshop, even farther than Hornheim, I think."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I knew I've never seen this place before... So it's really that far away?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "That's why it felt like I traveled really far when I left that place..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "So, this place feels far away for you, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I'm already tired. Well Sis, I..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, no! I still wanna talk...but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Nio!"
